{"tid":1980924,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【歌神效應】傳小鳳姐阿Lam攜手演抗疫騷，緊接阿Sam以歌為港人打氣","createTime":"2020-04-20T11:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T09:14:58.000Z","uid":35221,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b167dc9262a2d01811de634643573d7a08b1b9d7","tid":1980924,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:24:18.000Z","msg":"【歌神效應】傳徐小鳳林子祥攜手演抗疫騷　緊接許冠傑以歌為港人打氣<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;娛樂&nbsp;14:15&nbsp;2020/04/20&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2620000/2622295/lam_thumb_20200420_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2620000%2F2622295%2Flam_thumb_20200420_S_600.jpg&h=60f710cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌神許冠傑月初演出《2020同舟共濟Online Concert》，空前成功，演出錄逾600萬人次收看。有見及此，不少藝人在香港疫情下，均希望為港人打氣，繼古天樂演藝人協會在4月25日舉行網上抗疫騷外，今日有報導指兩位殿堂級歌手林子祥和徐小鳳都有意出山演打氣騷。<br />\n<br />\n許冠傑《2020同舟共濟Online Concert》，無論口碑、話題及觀看數字都造出漂亮成績，剛於上周六國際天后Lady Gaga發起《One World:Stay at Home》邀來陳奕迅、張學友網上演唱，亦掀起話題。多位歌手在疫情下都對網上音樂會甚有興趣，希望齊心以音樂抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2620000/2622295/lam20200420_886587676_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2620000%2F2622295%2Flam20200420_886587676_600.jpg&h=bdc76658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲&nbsp;林子祥有不少激昂人心作品。（東星圖片）<br />\n<br />\n今日有報導指，兩位殿堂級歌手林子祥和徐小鳳，近日就獲主辦商邀請，在疫境中出山為港人打氣，而兩位實力派巨星對此亦甚有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2620000/2622295/PaulaTsui20020420_65865228_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2620000%2F2622295%2FPaulaTsui20020420_65865228_600.jpg&h=5346dd76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲&nbsp;小鳳姐出山會否唱《喜氣洋洋》？（東星圖片）<br />\n<br />\n近年養尊處優的徐小鳳，由70年代起擁有不少勵志金曲，包括《風雨同路》、《順流逆流》等，其中《喜氣洋洋》更成網民至今依然力捧的神曲。<br />\n<br />\n小鳳姐近年每次舉行演唱會，都會有一輪捧飛潮，對上一次紅館騷是在18年9月，當時舉行六場演出，獲得不少圈中紅人捧場。<br />\n至於林子祥也有不少激昂人心歌曲如《男兒當自強》、《邁步向前》等，去年5月阿Lam舉行一連五場紅館《Lamusical演唱會》後，表示完成個唱後將會休息一段長時間，故阿Lam如出山，將是樂迷福氣。<br />\n<br />\n撰文 :&nbsp;TOPick柴犬出動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2622295/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%8C%E7%A5%9E%E6%95%88%E6%87%89%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%8F%E9%B3%B3%E6%9E%97%E5%AD%90%E7%A5%A5%E6%94%9C%E6%89%8B%E6%BC%94%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E9%A8%B7%E3%80%80%E7%B7%8A%E6%8E%A5%E8%A8%B1%E5%86%A0%E5%82%91%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%8C%E7%82%BA%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3?mtc=10030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2622295%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%258C%25E7%25A5%259E%25E6%2595%2588%25E6%2587%2589%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25BE%2590%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25B3%25B3%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25A5%25A5%25E6%2594%259C%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25BC%2594%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E5%2586%25A0%25E5%2582%2591%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25AD%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25B0%25A3%3Fmtc%3D10030&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPs3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=e418f683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2622295/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%8C%E7%A5%9E%E6%95%88%E6%87%89%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E5%BE%90%E5%B0%8F%E9%B3%B3%E6%9E%97%E5%AD%90%E7%A5%A5%E6%94%9C%E6%89%8B%E6%BC%94%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E9%A8%B7%E3%80%80%E7%B7%8A%E6%8E%A5%E8%A8%B1%E5%86%A0%E5%82%91%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%8C%E7%82%BA%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3?mtc=10030</a>"},{"pid":"0d07b34409bbd6c93f298acd739f14d48c519700","tid":1980924,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:56:23.000Z","msg":"有請<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0df4f7652ea4682160378769ed6eb21799a791","tid":1980924,"uid":313584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/ass